description:
In Decapolis Jordan, Jesus set free missionaries from demonic power. Using the men as a medium, the demon spoke to Jesus and asked to be cast into animals in the distance. A change then came over these men, they were now in their right minds. The demoniacs were healed by Jesus, and their first desire was to share the good news with others.
